// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Workspace Validation
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//
// Verify workspace is correctly configured:
//
//   go work sync          # Synchronize go.work.sum with module requirements
//   go build ./...        # Build all modules in workspace
//   go test ./...         # Test all modules in workspace
//   go mod tidy           # (In each module) Clean up dependencies
//
// Common Issues:
//
//   "module not found" - Check 'use' path is correct relative to go.work
//   "version mismatch" - Run 'go work sync' to resolve
//   "ambiguous import" - Ensure modules don't have conflicting package paths
//
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Modification Policy
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//
// Safe to Modify:
//   ✅ Add new 'use' directives for new modules
//   ✅ Remove 'use' directives for removed modules
//   ✅ Update Go version (ensure all modules support it)
//
// Modify with Care:
//   ⚠️ Changing module paths - may break imports
//   ⚠️ Removing shared modules - may break dependent modules
//
// NEVER Modify:
//   ❌ 4-block documentation structure
//   ❌ go.work.sum directly (auto-generated)
//
